short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for GitLab to create branches directly from issues

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Create a new branch from your issues so you can start programming right away. With this extension, you can quickly create a branch directly from the issue card. 

This extension adds an option to GitLab Issue Cards that allows you to create a branch directly from the target issue. After confirming the branch name, a new tab opens with all the preconfigured settings for creating a new branch.
